---
title: Double Herby Pork Steak & Potato Fries with Salsa Verde & Carrot Ribbon Salad
description: Savour the irresistible aroma of tender, juicy pork loin, marinated in garlic and herb and slathered in punchy salsa verde. A carrot ribbon salad served alondgside adds the perfect amount of crunchy texture and acidic brightness!

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with tomato due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6621ab959c7fd7890800a5b2-2a554a8f.jpeg
